Figure 2-5 I/O cable management spine and fiber cable organizer (rear view) 2.2 CPC drawer The IBM z16 Model A01 (machine type 3931) features some design changes (compared to IBM z15), primarily with the processor modules and memory packaging in the drawers. An IBM z16 A01 CPC drawer includes the following features:  Four Dual chip modules (DCMs)  Up to 48 Memory DIMMs  Symmetric multiprocessor (SMP) connectivity  Connectors to support PCIe+ Gen3 fan-out cards for PCIe+ I/O drawers or coupling fan-outs for coupling links to other
